{"tid":1363920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講明禁集會！即係727更加要人！","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:10:30.000Z","uid":123924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acbd5c79503aaf0087babff4730449ccc9b4d13d","tid":1363920,"uid":123924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:05:27.000Z","msg":"首先，大家唔好執著係咪遲咗出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTfFH1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTfFH1Y.png&h=461bb311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7GJFOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7GJFOE.png&h=08f1926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇返，黑警應該係base on下圖B款，唔好哂時間拗<br />\n<br />\n當務之急<br />\n一定！！一定！！一定！！要繼續號召<br />\n更加要講清楚係反對黑社會嘅遊行<br />\n要畀各界/外國知道<br />\n黑警禁止市民遊行反黑社會<br />\n鞏固遊行嘅合理理據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從而召集更多市民殺入元朗！！<br />\n<br />\n入到元朗<br />\n當日好有可能有兩個情況：<br />\n<br />\n1) 一入來屈你非法集會<br />\n到時係市民vs 黑警<br />\n點樣鬥黑警大家都有哂經驗<br />\n唔多講<br />\n<br />\n2) 黑警放手，由鄉黑睇場<br />\n到時情況一定混亂<br />\n但一定要夠多人<br />\n先至可以企穩陣腳<br />\n嚇窒班白衫<br />\n一定要齊裝，做足準備，隨時自衛反擊<br />\n大家開遮擋高空擲物<br />\n遇上白衫人攻擊<br />\n必定還拖！！<br />\n<br />\n同埋到時一定要計劃好撤退時間<br />\n避免一閂西鐵而一網成擒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請廣傳！！只有多人先可以保障大家安全！！</span>"},{"pid":"9f9e33ed3a44ac2303ac925db266c4ad31a4b131","tid":1363920,"uid":123924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}